{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSChipPicker"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"Tag"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Tag"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Hashable","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Each chip contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose choosen values through this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSFilterChip","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker itself does no have any defined accessiiblity value, label or identifier ; it remains in the users hands to define which one will be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However if defined in the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSCo